"{\"uid\": \"barrons.com-news-japan-s-kano-breaks-french-hearts-in-olympic-fencing-final-a1e082e8\", \"text\": \"Pirate IRWIN    Fencer Koki Kano became Japan's\\u00a0first individual epee Olympic champion on Sunday, beating France's Yannick Borel 15-9 as American defending champion Lee Kiefer won the women's foil.  The Barron's news department was not involved in the creation of the content above. This article was produced by AFP. For more information go toAFP.com.\\u00a9 Agence France-Presse\"}"